<h2> Let's talk about Rivers State </h2>
I'm practicing the different kinds of lists, so I'll be trying out ordered lists, unordered lists and definition lists. Let's start with the 23 Local governments in R/S. I'll present them in an ordered list. Here goes nothing!
<h3>LGAs in Rivers State </h3>
<ol>
  <li> Abual/Odual LGA </li> 
  <li> Ahoada East LGA </li>
  <li> Ahoada West LGA </li>
